data.description: This is a great opportunity to own a lovely 2-story brick home! An excellent location in Flowery Branch close to downtown, Lake Lanier, and shopping while also having the convenience of being close to 985. You’ll love this inviting and bright home featuring a spacious living area, foyer, half bath on main, and a fireplace for those cool nights. The kitchen offers a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and opens up to the dining room for an open concept design. This home gives the whole family plenty of space with large living spaces, bedrooms with dedicated closets. The oversized master bedroom has a sitting area and a master suite complete with walk-in closet, double vanity, stand alone shower, and soaking bathtub. Enjoy the seasons outdoors with a private backyard, featuring a covered patio, perfect for weekend barbecues and outdoor entertaining. Outdoor shed also provides additional storage for all your outdoor needs. Located in a great neighborhood! This home is a must-see with lots of curb appeal and a 2-car garage. Showings will begin on Tuesday, January 16th.
